text: Eadward cyningc gret ægelmer biscop & ælfgar eorl & ealle mine ðegenas & sciregerefan on Suthfolce & on Norðfolce & swa hwer swa Sancte Eadmund ænig land hafeþ freondlice.
& ic cyða eou þæt hic gehate be fullan hæse þæt Sancte Eadmundes inland sy scotfreo fram heregelde & fram eghwilc oðer gaful.
